data.description: Welcome home to this lovely three bedroom house in Hopewell Township!  This brick ranch creates simplicity and ease with single level living.  Enjoy the natural light that pours in throughout the home.  The large living room and dining room are fabulous for entertaining guests.  The flat private backyard is excellent for fall camp fires.  You'll love the large detached garage that is perfect for all your storage needs.  Just minutes from I376, shopping, community parks and more!  Don't miss your opportunity to live on a quiet street in a wonderful neighborhood!
